    <description>Editable campaign markers for Google Earth Pro. Add placemarks here — not under Campaign Board NetworkLinks in doc.kml (those are read-only). After editing: File → Save, then python3 scripts/sync_campaign_live.py --push and refresh Campaign Board links in doc.kml.</description>
